{"data":[{"date":"09:11 16/08","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \u201cNepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng Nepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng Nepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/HLV-Phan-Thanh-Hung-Nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Zing.vn: &quot;R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p \u00fd \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Nepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u00ean \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng cho h\u1ecd&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u00eam v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh n\u00f3i: &quot;Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t so v\u1edbi t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi chinh chi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i V.League, li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua. Sau n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi theo \u00f4ng, t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed7i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n nay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal &ndash; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 15/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\">U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nU23 Nepal, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng: Kiran Chemjong Limbu.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5554","checkdouble":"194590"},{"date":"11:05 16/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/2/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</h2><h2>Khi xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 xong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai h\u00f4m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 15/8. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 n\u00f3i: \u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Pakistan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-Co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0vs Olympic Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eaft b\u00e0i n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p Nepal, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Park c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong h\u00e0ng trung v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u1ee3i. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng. Ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Manh choi cuc hay trong tran tu ket voi U23 Iraq\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Iraq\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Hau-ve-Xuan-Manh-mong-mau-co-tien-thuong-de-tra-no-cho-bo-me-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng, v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7. \u00a0Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang d\u00e0nh cho \u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1n xuy\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Song r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i quen thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea9y V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm thay cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. L\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c anh v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Nepal: Kiran Chemjong, Tamang, Chaudhary, Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rohit Chand, Gurung, Bista, Magar, Bharat Khawas, Magar.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu-sao-khong-168-194536.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu-sao-khong-168-194536.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9, sao kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal: Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5553","checkdouble":"194598"},{"date":"11:38 16/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho hai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd t\u1edbi xem, ghi h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 6-0 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain h\u00f4m qua 15/8.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1edbi Indonesia v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5m HC v\u00e0ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ed1n n\u0103m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jo Hyeon-woo, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hwang Ui-jo v\u00e0 Son Heung-min - ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho r\u1eb1ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 Bahrain, Malaysia v\u00e0 Kyrgyzstan \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Vi\u1ec7t Nam, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng D, s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1ea5m HC v\u00e0ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam \u1edf Asiad 2018 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Park Hang-seo c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u01b0 li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c thu th\u1eadp video c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd di chuy\u1ec3n h\u01a1n 100 kilom\u00e9t t\u1eeb n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Cikarang, t\u1edbi Bandung \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Bahrain. Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd L\u01b0u Danh Minh xem v\u00e0 ghi ch\u00e9p v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Young Sub th\u00ec ghi h\u00ecnh to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/A1-3022-1534383659.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Young Sub khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111i Bandung ghi h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea1y, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 phi\u00ean d\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfng Anh cho HLV Park Hang-seo. \u1ea2nh Vnexpress</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang-seo kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u00f4m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Ngay c\u1ea3 Young Sub, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, c\u0169ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, \u0111i ghi h\u00ecnh theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y HLV Park Hang-seo c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i do th\u00e1m, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01a1i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u00e0 th\u1eafng Bahrain 6-0. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm l\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, n\u00ean r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D b\u1edfi trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pakistan 3-0 trong khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal. T\u1ed1i nay 16/8, Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong Nepal s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 HLV c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1. Khi \u0111\u00f3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c\u201d, HLV Park Hang-seo chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c e ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eed th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Vnexpress.net<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5552","checkdouble":"194601"},{"date":"09:25 16/08","title":"Griezmann: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/griezmann-toi-da-dung-khi-o-lai-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Griezmann kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>Atletico th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real</h2>\r\nGriezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barcelona trong v\u00f2ng 2 n\u0103m qua. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid trong m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. T\u1ea1i Nga, Grizou \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Les Bleus \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Griezmann T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Griezmann T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/griezmann-toi-da-dung-khi-o-lai-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGriezmann kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho Atletico \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00eam qua v\u1edbi Real. Anh ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 57 ph\u00fat do th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c ch\u01b0a \u1ed5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Diego Costa v\u00e0 hai b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Saul v\u00e0 Koke trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Atletico gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng vang d\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real.\r\n<h2>Griezmann vui m\u1eebng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\nHLV Diego Simeone gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Atletico v\u1edbi 7 danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 Griezmann ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng ni\u1ec1m tin \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Simeone l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u00e0o Simeone. H\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t 100% th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5551","checkdouble":"194588"},{"date":"09:50 16/08","title":"Simeone n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Real \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/simeone-noi-gi-sau-dai-thang-real-o-sieu-cup-chau-au.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real, HLV Simeone kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y l\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Atletico.</h2><h2>Atletico th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u01b0u th\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Atletico. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o s\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ngay t\u1eeb gi\u00e2y th\u1ee9 49 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian sau \u0111\u00f3, Real \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Benzema v\u00e0 Ramos. Nh\u01b0ng khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ebft th\u00fac th\u00ec Costa m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Atletico \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Saul v\u00e0 Koke \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<h2>Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Real \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Real \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/simeone-noi-gi-sau-dai-thang-real-o-sieu-cup-chau-au.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Simeone kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Atletico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Simeone kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Atletico ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb mang l\u1ea1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi. Sau b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng. N\u1ebfu t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u00e0y v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edb l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. M\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng. Sau tr\u1eadn thua t\u1ea1i Milan (chung k\u1ebft C1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real), t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap t\u00f4i tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Valencia\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diego-costa-no-to-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-real-madrid-184-194584.html\">Diego Costa n\u1ed5 to sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc-180-194576.html\">Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5550","checkdouble":"194592"},{"date":"11:58 16/08","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n 2 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/lo-dien-2-ung-vien-hang-dau-cho-chuc-giam-doc-ky-thuat-tai-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man Utd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt (hay c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1). Trong \u0111\u00f3 2 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Dan Ashworth v\u00e0 Paul Mitchell.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong tu\u1ea7n qua, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh loan tin Man Utd s\u1eafp s\u1eeda cho kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c danh Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. Ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Sir Alex Ferguson v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u00ec \u1edf M.U \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y b\u1edfi Sir Alex \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch lu\u00f4n c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV. C\u00e1i l\u1ec7 \u0111\u00f3 duy tr\u00ec cho \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd d\u00f9 sau khi Sir Alex ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thay t\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n (David Moyes, Louis Van Gaal v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Jose Mourinho).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c danh n\u00e0y v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed1i k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u1eefa HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n 2 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt MU c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n 2 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt MU c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/23BF4E8900000578-0-image-m-55_1421794323923.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dan Ashworth</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim, BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt chuy\u00ean tr\u00e1ch. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Sky Sports th\u00ec 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 Man Utd nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Dan Ashworth v\u00e0 Paul Mitchell, hai g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m tr\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y \u1edf Old Trafford. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDan Ashworth \u0111ang l\u00e0m Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Anh (FA). \u00d4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u201c\u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n\" \u0111\u1eb1ng sau gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong 2 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i tr\u1ebb. C\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a \u0110TQG\u00a0Anh c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o m\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o khi m\u00e0 Tam s\u01b0 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh thu\u1ed9c di\u1ec7n th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Dan Ashworth l\u00e0 \u201cDNA Anh\u201d, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf m\u1ecdi l\u1ee9a tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0103n t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3,\u00a0 Paul Mitchell l\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia \u201cs\u0103n \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf Anh. \u00d4ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Manchester, t\u1eebng l\u00e0m tr\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u00f3m truy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u1edf Spurs v\u00e0 Southampton. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Paul Mitchell \u0111ang gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf RB Leipzig.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra Sadio Mane, Dejan Lovren, Nathaniel Clyne \u1edf Southampton v\u00e0 Dele Alli, Toby Alderweireld, Heung-Min Son v\u00e0 Kieran Trippier \u1edf Tottenham sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/gerrard-tham-vong-duoc-lam-hlv-man-utd-172-194569.html\">Gerrard tham v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m HLV\u2026 Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-don-day-du-trong-phao-tro-lai-cuoi-tuan-nay-172-194567.html\">Man Utd \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-man-utd-tri-an-mourinho-sau-khi-ra-di-172-194564.html\">Sao Man Utd tri \u00e2n Mourinho sau khi ra \u0111i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-tre-quyet-tam-roi-bo-man-utd-mai-mai-172-194559.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Man Utd m\u00e3i m\u00e3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-vui-tu-hang-cong-truoc-tran-gap-brighton-172-194551.html\">MU \u0111\u00f3n tin vui t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brighton</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea-172-194549.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\">Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5549","checkdouble":"194603"},{"date":"07:33 16/08","title":"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/sieu-sao-ronaldo-lai-ghi-ban-trong-mau-ao-juventus.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><h2>Si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u1edbi &quot;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin&quot; b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 5-0 t\u1ea1i Villas Peros v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 8-0, \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00e1c v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Villas Peros, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c k\u00edn t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, CR7 nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec \u1edf m\u1ee9c cao nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p vi\u1ec7c anh v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o d\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Ronaldo, tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1eeba qua c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 Leonardo Bonucci hay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Joao Cancelo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Serie A 2018/19 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh. M\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 SV\u0110 Marc'Antonio Bentegodi b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khi Juventus h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chievo Verona.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5548","checkdouble":"194582"},{"date":"07:35 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal: Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ra sao m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i qua 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh Nepal v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mitoma. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u00ean BXH khi c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Nhat-Ban-thang-nhe-Nepal-Thoi-co-vang-cho-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng&nbsp; s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng D, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef v\u1eefng ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Th\u1eadt may quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong tay th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal l\u00fac 19h00. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n \u0111i xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Vi\u1ec7t Nam li\u1ec7u &ldquo;c\u00f3 c\u1eeda&rdquo; tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o ch\u1ec9 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U21, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Nhat Ban 1-0 Nepal\" title=\"Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 1-0 Nepal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/391440693146215057728883752561219127476224n-1534251167958226252819.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (xanh) g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean song c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng x\u00e9 l\u01b0\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh Nepal. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi, l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Nepal \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 c\u00f3 63% th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ebfn 22 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n, s\u00fat c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn 13 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eed th\u1ee7. Do \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 ngang ng\u1eeda v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Goc-nhin-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu,-sao-khong-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV&nbsp;Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Pakistan, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Wibawa Mukti \u0111\u1ec3 do th\u00e1m Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u00d4ng c\u00f9ng tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Lee Young Jin, L\u01b0 \u0110\u00ecnh Tu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 phi\u00ean d\u1ecbch Lee Young Sub&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u kh\u00e1 t\u1ef7 m\u1ec9 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ch\u1ebf s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, NHM Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD. Song \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc &lsquo;v\u1eadt c\u1ea3n&rsquo; \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean mang t\u00ean Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eady, c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda c\u1ea1nh tranh danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 15/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/olympic-nepal-dat-muc-tieu-co-diem-truoc-olympic-viet-nam-472-194532.html\">Olympic Nepal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018-168-194524.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018-168-194524.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khen ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 theo d\u00f5i s\u00e1t sao c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 14/8, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#xA;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5547","checkdouble":"194550"},{"date":"07:33 16/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.</h2><h2>Ba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u00fang ta ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal,-(19h-ngay-168)-Duy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Nepal kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, Nepal kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ea7y kinh nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c v\u00e0 v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Olympic Nepal t\u1edbi t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00edt t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb,&nbsp;m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i Th\u1ec3 thao Nam \u00c1 \u1edf Bangladesh v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018, Olympic Nepal v\u1eeba c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn thua tan t\u00e1c 0-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iraq, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Kuwait v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 13 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2014. Nh\u1eefng d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>H\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Nepal v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Khi \u1ea5y, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed an to\u00e0n gi\u00fap Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 15/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 v\u1eady n\u00ean Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 16/8. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay c\u1ea3 khi tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 168) Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-(19h-ngay-168)-Duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1ef1 tin trong cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o ch\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Olympic Nepal. Theo chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng Park c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hai nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef s\u1ee9c cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3 ng\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t trong hai l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ho\u1eb7c V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park cho ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, V\u0103n To\u00e0n hay Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi b\u1ecb \u0111au nh\u1eb9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Quang H\u1ea3i ho\u1eb7c \u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u1edf trung t\u00e2m tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1p m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Nepal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, vi\u1ec7c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i Nepal \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u tay. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, v\u00ec th\u1ebf h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 v\u1eady th\u00ec Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong l\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, NHM Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Nepal: Kiran Chemjong, Tamang, Chaudhary, Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rohit Chand, Gurung, Bista, Magar, Bharat Khawas, Magar.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: 3-0</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 15/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-han-quoc-noi-gi-ve-man-ra-quan-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194540.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo?</span><br>\r\nB\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung-168-194506.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-khoi-dau-ruc-ro-nhung-168-194506.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan: Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u01b0ng&hellip;</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:&#10;10.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5546","checkdouble":"194581"},{"date":"08:57 16/08","title":"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/7/8/hlv-olympic-thai-lan-quyet-gianh-3-diem-dau-tien.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Uzbekistan v\u00e0 Qatar, Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Olympic Bangladesh.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/24/HLV-Olympic-Thai-Lan-quyet-gianh-3-diem-dau-tien-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Worrawoot Srimaka quy\u1ebft gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Bangladesh\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u nay (16/8, gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bangladesh. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, HLV Worrawoot Srimaka \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi c\u01a1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t. Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m qua, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 nh\u1eb1m h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOlympic Bangladesh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam \u00c1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Nepal. S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh to cao. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, sau khi xem Bangladesh thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Uzbekistan, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nOlympic Th\u00e1i Lan ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1 ra l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bangladesh, Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a Qatar trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. V\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ngay c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng h\u1ea1ng 3 chung cu\u1ed9c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 1 trong 4 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5545","checkdouble":"194587"},{"date":"08:23 16/08","title":"Diego Costa \"n\u1ed5\" to sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/diego-costa-no-to-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Costa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Atletico Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai sau khi gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.</h2><h2>Atletico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Costa gi\u00fap Atletico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Real Madrid \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00eam qua. T\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c t\u1ea1i Tallinn l\u00e0 4-2 sau khi hai hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDiego Costa \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhanh nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 49 gi\u00e2y sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i c\u00f2i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. 26 ph\u00fat sau, Karim Benzema g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ramos \u0111\u01b0a Real v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 71 t\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u1ee7a Estonia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Costa \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Atletico v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. V\u00e0 hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Saul Niguez v\u00e0 Koke \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Atletico gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ee9 7 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc-180-194576.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Diego Simeone</span>.</div>\r\n<h2>Costa n\u1ed5 to\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Diego Costa ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/diego-costa-no-to-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Diego Costa t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;V\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd t\u1eeb l\u00e2u. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Real \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Atletico lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tham v\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u nh\u1edd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc-180-194576.html\">Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5544","checkdouble":"194584"},{"date":"08:29 16/08","title":"Real Madrid g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico: Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/real-madrid-thua-atletico-madrid-khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ed7i nh\u1edb l\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t sau tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n.</h2><h2>\u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc Sergio Ramos th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf ph\u00fat 63, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng Los Blancos s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ba n\u0103m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 mi\u1ec1n k\u00fd \u1ee9c t\u1eebng r\u1ea5t th\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i gi\u1eadt m\u00ecnh nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zidane kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n Cristiano Ronaldo n\u1eefa.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-thua-Atletico-Madrid-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sergio Ramos t\u1eebng g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 Real Madrid \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00e1u ph\u00fat sau, Diego Costa \u0111\u01b0a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i, m\u1edf ra c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho Los Blancos. Nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e2ng c\u00fap v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua 4 b\u00e0n, nhi\u1ec1u Madridista tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Le Coq Arena (Tallinn, Estonia) \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y ba th\u00e1ng th\u00f4i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111ang ng\u00e2y ng\u1ea5t men say chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1ec9nh cao xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ef1c s\u00e2u. S\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh v\u00eanh trong l\u00f2ng n\u1eeda tr\u1eafng th\u00e0nh Madrid th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3. \u0110\u1ed5i l\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u &quot;ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn&quot; c\u00f3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb Zizou, hay ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1edb th\u00eam?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Real-Madrid-guc-nga-truoc-Atletico-Khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Julen Lopetegui ch\u01b0a kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb Zizou sau khi Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi s\u1ebd nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 hai. Lopetegui ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0o trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Gareth Bale ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Los Blancos m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lopetegui sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh Real Madrid hai tay d\u00e2ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng t\u1ef1 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 Los Blancos l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u sai l\u1ea7m h\u01a1n, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 xin th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea7u tr\u1eddi?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Zizou l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau ch\u00edn n\u0103m, Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o mang v\u1ec1 cho h\u1ecd 50 b\u00e0n m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a n\u1eefa, Cristiano Ronaldo gi\u1edd s\u1ebd s\u0103n b\u00e0n cho Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo muon chia tay Real tu lau\" title=\"Ronaldo muon chia tay Real tu lau\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/kroos-qua-kho-de-thay-the-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Real Madrid v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ngu\u00f4i n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb Cristiano Ronaldo.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo c\u00f2n m\u1edf l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Marcelo sang Juventus. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u1ea7y l\u1ea5p l\u1eedng r\u1eb1ng &quot;gi\u1edd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y&quot;. Ch\u00ednh Marcelo m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 c\u1ee7a Diego Costa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric &quot;ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A&quot; theo l\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. Modric kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5u \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Inter Milan. Th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, c\u00f2n ai s\u1ebd ra \u0111i n\u1eefa?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Thibaut Courtois c\u00f3 l\u1ebd n\u00e9 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico, c\u00f2n Vinicius \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid trong tran tranh Sieu cup chau Au 2018.\" title=\"Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/real-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Real Madrid thua Atletico Madrid trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGareth Bale ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo. S\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u Bale c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu khi qu\u00e1 m\u1eabn c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 26 tr\u1eadn, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa ch\u1ec9 19 tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n tr\u00f4i sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng th\u00ec giao h\u1eefu c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0... giao h\u1eefu. Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4i, Julen Lopetegui nh\u1eadn ra \u00f4ng c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diego-costa-no-to-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-real-madrid-184-194584.html\">Diego Costa n\u1ed5 to sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/bang-vinh-danh-thibaut-courtois-bi-pha-hoai-180-194580.html\">B\u1ea3ng vinh danh Thibaut Courtois b\u1ecb C\u0110V Atletico Madrid ph\u00e1 ho\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc-180-194576.html\">Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico: Ma c\u0169 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t ma m\u1edbi, Atletico l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ramos-tran-an-courtois-truoc-man-ra-mat-lan-lon-cam-xuc-172-194531.html\">Ramos tr\u1ea5n an Courtois tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5543","checkdouble":"194585"},{"date":"08:56 16/08","title":"Real thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t, Casemiro v\u1eabn b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/casemiro-real-khong-co-gi-de-bao-chua-cho-that-bai-truoc-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Casemiro \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o HLV Lopetegui b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i m\u00e0 Real v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><h2>Real thua \u0111\u1eafng Atletico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Atletico Madrid. V\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Tallinn v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 4-2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. Atletico Madrid v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean ch\u1ec9 sau 49 gi\u00e2y v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Costa. Nh\u01b0ng Real \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u1edbi hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Benzema v\u00e0 Ramos. \u0110\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Diego Costa m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Atletico. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Atletico ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n nh\u1edd th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Saul v\u00e0 Koke.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Casemiro b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Casemiro b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui sau tr\u1eadn thua mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Casemiro b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui sau tr\u1eadn thua mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/casemiro-real-khong-co-gi-de-bao-chua-cho-that-bai-truoc-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Casemiro b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Lopetegui sau tr\u1eadn thua Atletico</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn cho HLV Lopetegui tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Bernd Schuster n\u0103m 2007.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Casemiro v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Lopetegui c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 anh \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n. Ronaldo gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9. HLV Lopetegui \u0111ang l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef \u00e1nh h\u00e0o quang cho Real v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 4 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League trong 5 n\u0103m qua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 Lopetegui \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd ch\u00ed chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eabn c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Lopetegui. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico: Ma c\u0169 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t ma m\u1edbi, Atletico l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong> </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5542","checkdouble":"194586"}]}